Voluntary undertakings
Without limiting the matters to which the voluntary undertaking may relate, the voluntary undertaking may include any of the following undertakings by the organisation or person concerned:
(a) an undertaking to take specified action within a specified time;
(b) an undertaking to refrain from taking specified action;
(c) an undertaking to publicise the voluntary undertaking.

